{
  "id": "bad-deploy-001",
  "version": 1,
  "title": "壊れたデプロイの夜",
  "difficulty": "intermediate",
  "timeLimitMinutes": 10,
  "service": {
    "name": "やまびこ API",
    "healthUrl": "http://localhost:8080/health"
  },
  "briefing": [
    "デプロイ直後に 5xx が出たら、まず「直前に何が変わったか」を疑う。",
    "deploy.log とアプリ設定、そして前リリースとの差分が手がかり。",
    "切り戻し(ロールバック)は立派な暫定復旧。"
  ],
  "startup": [
    {
      "id": "api",
      "command": "PORT=8080 node /workspace/services/yamabiko-api/server.mjs",
      "waitForPort": 8080
    },
    {
      "id": "fake-db",
      "command": "node /workspace/services/fake-db/server.mjs",
      "waitForPort": 15432
    }
  ],
  "topology": {
    "nodes": [
      {
        "id": "user",
        "label": "ユーザー",
        "kind": "external"
      },
      {
        "id": "api",
        "label": "やまびこ API",
        "kind": "service",
        "processId": "api"
      },
      {
        "id": "fake-db",
        "label": "疑似データベース",
        "kind": "datastore",
        "processId": "fake-db"
      }
    ],
    "edges": [
      {
        "from": "user",
        "to": "api"
      },
      {
        "from": "api",
        "to": "fake-db"
      }
    ]
  },
  "triggers": [
    {
      "id": "bad-deploy",
      "atMs": 45000,
      "type": "bad_deploy",
      "params": {}
    }
  ],
  "alerts": [
    {
      "id": "deploy-500",
      "atMs": 70000,
      "severity": "critical",
      "message": "HTTP 500 spike after deploy",
      "source": "scenario"
    }
  ],
  "successConditions": [
    {
      "type": "http_status",
      "url": "http://localhost:8080/health",
      "status": 200
    },
    {
      "type": "process_running",
      "processId": "api"
    }
  ],
  "runbooks": [
    {
      "id": "runbook.deploy",
      "title": "デプロイ起因障害の初動",
      "body": "1. /workspace/logs/deploy.log で直近のデプロイ時刻とバージョンを確認する\n2. エラーログ(app.log)の内容を読み、どこへの接続が失敗しているか把握する\n3. アプリ設定 /workspace/etc/yamabiko-api.json を開き、前リリース\n   (/workspace/releases/yamabiko-api.previous.json)と見比べる\n4. 切り戻す(前リリースの設定を書き戻す)か、設定を修正する\n5. curl localhost:8080/health で復旧確認する(設定は自動反映、再起動不要)"
    }
  ],
  "chatMessages": [
    {
      "id": "boss-deploy",
      "atMs": 95000,
      "from": "上司",
      "body": "さっきのデプロイ？僕は何も変えてないよ。おやすみ。"
    }
  ],
  "navigationSteps": [
    {
      "id": "nav-5xx",
      "atMs": 0,
      "hint": "HTTP 5xx が上がっていないか監視画面で確認する",
      "panel": "metrics"
    },
    {
      "id": "nav-deploy-log",
      "atMs": 50000,
      "hint": "直近のデプロイ履歴を確認する",
      "panel": "terminal",
      "suggestedCommand": "tail /workspace/logs/deploy.log"
    },
    {
      "id": "nav-config",
      "atMs": 80000,
      "hint": "設定を前リリースと見比べる",
      "panel": "editor"
    }
  ]
}
